{"tid":2412043,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"索羅斯曾稱後悔投資Pltr 持股上季賺近2.6億美元","createTime":"2021-02-17T19:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T14:25:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe9c140fcccd420d465f4529e35376dc9dee8c3","tid":2412043,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T19:30:12.000Z","msg":"1筆讓「金融巨鱷」索羅斯（George Soros）感到後悔的投資，讓這名億萬富豪上季進帳近2.6億美元（約73.79億元台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n根據周二提交監管機關的文件，索羅斯旗下投資公司索羅斯基金管理（Soros Fund Management）截至去年底持有近1846萬股資料探勘業者Palantir科技公司股票，數量與去年第3季持平。不過，索羅斯持有的Palantir股票截至去年底價值近4.35億美元，高於去年第3季的1.75億美元左右。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，索羅斯基金管理去年11月在聲明中表示，該公司最近未買進Palantir股票，首次投資Palantir的時間是2012年，索羅斯基金管理對決定投資Palantir感到後悔。索羅斯基金管理當時表示，已拋售所有該公司允許賣出的股票，索羅斯基金管理會繼續拋售該股。<br />\n<br />\n索羅斯基金管理說：「索羅斯基金管理是在未充分理解大數據負面社會影響時投資Palantir&hellip;索羅斯基金管理不認同Palantir商業策略。」<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210218/E4SKATF7SNECTH3ZS6DUETLGBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210218%2FE4SKATF7SNECTH3ZS6DUETLGBA%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=2ccaa0fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210218%2FE4SKATF7SNECTH3ZS6DUETLGBA%2F&h=5abc27a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210218/E4SKATF7SNECTH3ZS6DUETLGBA/</a>"},{"pid":"3e0d6448052730415cc45f9c4d19796c5a8a5b69","tid":2412043,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T19:49:46.000Z","msg":"大戶講嘢要掉轉黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eef1efe5b839e4795a86eea9b611e3ef702e87f","tid":2412043,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T19:55:38.000Z","msg":"死廢老 唔係好彩佢食谷種啦"},{"pid":"0881820b7fbb6989cb700dcc24a161ae1af95d27","tid":2412043,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T14:25:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死廢老"}